 "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015388, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O He who exists and existed and there is none like Him. O He who shall not perish and none shall survive but Your Irresistible Face. O He for whom „thunder repeateth His praises, and so do the angels, with awe: O He who answers whenever called! O He who has Mercy when asked for! O He whose attribute of Grandeur those who extol cannot comprehend! O He Whom no vision comprehends, but He Comprehends all vision. And He is the Knower of Subtleties, the All-Aware.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "YAA MAN KAANA WA YAKOO-NO WA LAIY-SA KAMIS-LEHI SHAIY-OON YAA MAN LAA YAMOO-TO WA LAA YABQAA ILLAA WAJHO-HUL JABBAA-RO YAA MAIY-YO-SABBE-HUR RA’DO BE-HAMDE-HI WAL MALAA-E-KATO MIN KHAIY-FATE-HI YAA MIN IZAA DO-E’E AJAA-BA WA YAA MAN EE-ZAS TUR-HEMA WA YAA MAN LAA YUDRE-KUL WAASE-FOONA SEFA-TA-HU MIN A’Z-MATE-HI YAA MAL-LAA TUDRE KOHUL AB-SAARO WA HOWA YUDRE-KUL AB-SAARA WA HOWAL LATEE-FUL KHABEE-RO.", "ArabicText1": "يَا مَنْ كَانَ وَيَكُوْنُ وَلَيْسَ كَمِثْلِهٖ شَيْءٌ يَا مَنْ لَا يَمُوْتُ وَلَا يَبْقٰى اِلَّا وَجْهُهُ الْجَبَّارُ يَا مَنْ يُّسَبِّحُ الرَّعْدُ بِحَمْدِهٖ وَالْمَلَائِكَةُ مِنْ خِيْفَتِهٖ يَا مِنْ اِذَا دُعِيْ اَجَابَ وَيَا مَنْ اِذَا اسْتُرْحِمَ رَحِمَ وَيَا مَنْ لَا يُدْرِكُ الْوَاصِفُوْنَ صِفَتَهٗ مِنْ عَظَمَتِهٖ يَا مَنْ لَّا تُدْرِكُهُ الْاَبْصَارُ وَهُوَ يُدْرِكُ الْاَبْصَارَ وَهُوَ اللَّطِيْفُ الْخَبِيْرُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign